# CODEOWNERS
# 
# This file defines code ownership for the Finance Backoffice Report project.
# When a Pull Request modifies files, GitHub will automatically request reviews
# from the code owners listed here.
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Format: <file-pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Owners must be GitHub usernames (@username) or teams (@org/team-name)
#
# Rules are evaluated from bottom to top, so the last matching pattern takes precedence.
# More specific rules should be placed at the bottom of the file.

